WEBVTT

01:34.360 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:38.640
‪YIHE UNIVERSITY

01:38.720 --> 01:40.320
I received the postgraduate
exam materials this morning.

01:40.400 --> 01:41.440
I didn't expect so much.

01:41.520 --> 01:43.320
I plan to check them out
back in my hometown.

01:43.400 --> 01:44.520
Thanks for helping me.

01:44.600 --> 01:45.680
You're welcome.

01:45.760 --> 01:47.000
By the way, Yifan, do you want
to take the postgraduate exam?

01:47.080 --> 01:48.520
We could study for it together.

01:49.440 --> 01:51.280
I'm thinking of getting a job.

01:51.360 --> 01:52.600
I'm planning to go back home
for graduate school.

01:52.680 --> 01:54.320
My boyfriend is still waiting for me.

01:54.400 --> 01:55.480
I see you're alone.

01:55.560 --> 01:57.200
Isn't there someone waiting for you, too?

01:58.560 --> 02:01.240
I just feel that if I go back home,

02:01.320 --> 02:04.520
I can be a little spoiled
and eat and drink with my parents.

02:04.600 --> 02:05.880
How great is that!

02:06.560 --> 02:07.520
It's this one.

02:07.600 --> 02:10.039
Sir! Could you please open the trunk?

02:13.680 --> 02:15.280
Yifan, just leave it here.
I'll call the driver.

02:22.440 --> 02:25.560
Sir, can you open the trunk, please?

02:34.800 --> 02:36.000
Thank you.

02:41.080 --> 02:42.280
So much stuff.

02:43.400 --> 02:44.760
Thank you, sir.

02:59.720 --> 03:00.920
3,430 DAYS

03:02.200 --> 03:05.680
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

03:13.520 --> 03:15.480
‪SANG YAN

03:15.560 --> 03:17.440
I'm working overtime. I'll be back late.

03:17.520 --> 03:18.360
WEN YIFAN

03:18.440 --> 03:20.160
You've been working overtime
for several days.

03:20.680 --> 03:21.960
Take care of yourself.

03:27.480 --> 03:28.520
I've got some food.

03:28.600 --> 03:30.400
Just heat it up and eat when you're back.

03:31.600 --> 03:32.680
I left takeout for you.

03:32.760 --> 03:34.040
Remember to eat when you get back.

03:43.280 --> 03:45.320
DON'T OVERWORK. TAKE CARE

03:45.400 --> 03:47.000
When will you come home?

03:50.160 --> 03:51.520
I left some late-night snacks for you.

03:55.720 --> 03:57.480
I'm going on a business trip tomorrow
for an interview.

03:58.240 --> 04:00.200
Wen Shuangjiang, you're back!

04:03.960 --> 04:05.320
Are you back?

04:10.760 --> 04:12.040
I'm back!

04:51.440 --> 04:53.280
SLEEP EARLY

04:53.360 --> 04:55.240
WHEN WILL YOU BE BACK?

04:59.160 --> 05:00.800
AROUND TWO OR THREE

05:38.720 --> 05:41.680
- Hello?
- Yifan, are you at home?

05:43.000 --> 05:45.440
We'll be downstairs in three minutes.
We're coming to pick you up now.

05:52.520 --> 05:53.800
Oh, you're back.

05:58.080 --> 05:59.280
Are you tired?

06:00.400 --> 06:02.120
What about you? Are you tired?

06:02.200 --> 06:03.760
I have to head out for a while.

06:04.520 --> 06:05.760
Going out again?

06:05.840 --> 06:07.000
There's an unexpected situation.

06:07.720 --> 06:08.720
- Let me drive you.
- No need.

06:08.800 --> 06:09.680
Ms. Qian is waiting for me downstairs.

06:09.760 --> 06:10.680
I want to drive you.

06:10.760 --> 06:12.320
Hurry and get some rest. It's too late.

06:26.280 --> 06:27.240
What a coincidence, Yifan.

06:27.320 --> 06:29.800
This time, the news
happened near your place.

06:29.880 --> 06:31.240
Didn't you hear
the police sirens just now?

06:31.320 --> 06:32.400
No.

06:34.040 --> 06:35.480
What happened?

06:35.560 --> 06:36.800
It's not a big story.

06:36.880 --> 06:38.520
It's just a bit strange.

06:38.600 --> 06:39.760
Be serious.

06:39.840 --> 06:41.480
A car accident isn't a big news story?

06:41.560 --> 06:44.560
And I heard both the driver
and the passenger were injured.

06:45.120 --> 06:48.640
The most shocking part is the car
went straight into a noodle shop.

06:48.720 --> 06:50.120
That's astonishing!

06:52.720 --> 06:56.920
DRAGON KING NOODLE SHOP

07:05.640 --> 07:07.600
- Someone's in there?
- Yes!

07:11.640 --> 07:12.720
Hurry up.

07:12.800 --> 07:14.720
Long, park the car
in the parking lot later.

07:14.800 --> 07:16.600
- Don't block traffic here.
- Okay.

07:19.080 --> 07:21.080
This is truly unbelievable.

07:21.160 --> 07:23.680
I heard this is a second-hand car
that's almost junk.

07:23.760 --> 07:25.000
The driver, not sure what happened,

07:25.080 --> 07:28.120
drove it right into the noodle shop
while maneuvering.

07:28.200 --> 07:30.560
The person is still in the car.
No one knows how they're doing.

07:30.640 --> 07:31.560
Well,

07:32.160 --> 07:35.600
should this be treated as a joke
or as a disaster news story?

07:35.680 --> 07:36.640
Stop joking around.

07:36.720 --> 07:40.360
Remember this. You must get
a clear shot of the driver's face.

07:40.440 --> 07:42.680
But you need to consider
the interviewee's mood.

07:42.760 --> 07:44.160
If they don't want to be interviewed,

07:44.240 --> 07:45.200
try to avoid it.

07:45.280 --> 07:46.360
- Is that okay?
- Okay.

07:46.440 --> 07:47.640
Go ahead. Get to work.

07:53.440 --> 07:54.680
- They're out!
- They're out!

07:55.360 --> 07:56.640
What's going on?

07:56.720 --> 07:57.800
It's nothing. I'm fine.

07:57.880 --> 07:58.880
Have you been drinking?

07:59.400 --> 08:00.520
What's going on?

08:02.120 --> 08:03.960
We're just waiting for this shot.

08:04.040 --> 08:05.880
Right here.

08:13.120 --> 08:14.640
What are you doing?

09:52.120 --> 09:53.440
GOOD NEWS, PARIS, BEIJING, MOSCOW

09:53.520 --> 09:55.320
Fortunately,
the driver isn't seriously injured.

09:55.400 --> 09:57.440
The damages caused by the man

09:57.520 --> 09:59.680
are initially estimated at 140,000 yuan.

09:59.760 --> 10:01.240
The price he paid is quite high.

10:01.320 --> 10:04.720
This news was reported
by Wen Yifan from Nanwu TV.

10:06.840 --> 10:08.400
Okay, let me adjust.

10:12.000 --> 10:13.520
Did he see me?

10:21.240 --> 10:22.400
Sorry,

10:22.480 --> 10:24.640
I… I want to add one more thing.

10:28.680 --> 10:30.320
Fortunately,
the driver isn't seriously injured.

10:30.400 --> 10:34.520
The damages caused by the man
are initially estimated at 140,000 yuan.

10:34.600 --> 10:36.200
The price he paid is quite high.

10:37.360 --> 10:40.240
This news was reported by Nanwu TV.

11:02.080 --> 11:03.560
Why are you still awake?

11:05.560 --> 11:07.120
Isn't today Saturday?

11:09.440 --> 11:10.400
I'm about to sleep.

11:16.840 --> 11:17.960
But you

11:18.480 --> 11:20.080
should finish
your porridge before sleeping.

11:24.360 --> 11:25.400
What's wrong?

11:26.640 --> 11:27.800
Something bad happened?

11:34.240 --> 11:35.840
I'm so tired. I don't want to move at all.

11:44.800 --> 11:47.800
Then, hold me like this,
and you won't be tired anymore.

11:51.120 --> 11:52.360
Drink your porridge first.

11:52.880 --> 11:53.840
It'll get cold soon.

11:55.160 --> 11:57.320
Later, you can hold me however you want.

11:58.440 --> 12:01.040
I'll even hold you while you sleep
if you want. Is that okay?

12:08.240 --> 12:09.360
Sang Yan…

12:14.880 --> 12:16.920
I won't be like before.

12:18.080 --> 12:19.600
I won't anymore.

12:22.040 --> 12:23.480
I'll treat you well.

12:24.520 --> 12:26.240
I won't hurt you again.

12:27.960 --> 12:30.560
I want to be with you every day.

12:31.840 --> 12:34.280
I don't want to see
those people from before.

12:34.360 --> 12:35.920
Not a single one.

12:36.960 --> 12:39.400
So, can we always be like this?

12:40.240 --> 12:42.040
Can you stay with me always?

12:44.480 --> 12:45.960
When you want to talk,

12:47.160 --> 12:48.040
remember to call me.

13:03.600 --> 13:04.800
I want to kiss you.

13:17.240 --> 13:18.560
I'll go rest now.

13:20.080 --> 13:21.120
Wen Shuangjiang.

13:29.960 --> 13:31.160
Does this count as a kiss?

13:39.640 --> 13:40.920
It's not the first time.

13:42.920 --> 13:44.200
So,

13:49.840 --> 13:51.040
I'm not being frivolous, right?

13:55.360 --> 13:56.880
What kind of fate is this for me?

13:58.160 --> 13:59.800
Being kissed and hugged by you this early.

14:00.560 --> 14:02.120
And you kissed, but not properly.

14:04.680 --> 14:05.520
Wen Shuangjiang,

14:08.120 --> 14:09.760
if you want to flirt,

14:11.600 --> 14:12.520
can you be serious about it?

14:13.840 --> 14:15.640
How can I be serious?

14:17.840 --> 14:18.680
Look at me properly.

14:24.640 --> 14:25.560
Come closer and speak.

14:31.120 --> 14:32.200
Then?

14:52.440 --> 14:53.800
And I'm hooked.

15:38.640 --> 15:40.280
What's wrong? Why are you hiding?

15:41.880 --> 15:43.200
I'm a bit shy.

15:48.280 --> 15:49.560
Are you hungry?

15:59.200 --> 16:01.960
I can't do both at the same time.

16:03.240 --> 16:04.800
Do you want to drink porridge first,

16:05.560 --> 16:06.840
or should I

16:07.880 --> 16:08.720
kiss you a little longer?

16:12.760 --> 16:14.000
Let's drink the porridge first.

16:44.880 --> 16:46.080
Go rest after eating.

16:46.600 --> 16:48.000
You still need to go to work later, right?

16:54.600 --> 16:56.120
You want to continue?

17:06.720 --> 17:07.800
Your kissing skills are so terrible.

17:09.160 --> 17:10.200
My lips hurt.

17:12.640 --> 17:14.599
- Well, I just…
- Need to practice more.

17:51.000 --> 17:53.320
So, "Laughter" was Grandma's nickname.

17:54.720 --> 17:56.520
Do you know where Grandpa
spent all the money

17:56.600 --> 17:57.920
the last six months?

18:02.240 --> 18:05.560
He's been spending it
on those dancing aunties, right?

18:07.240 --> 18:08.920
Grandpa missed the days

18:09.000 --> 18:10.800
when he was with Grandma,
living a simple life,

18:10.880 --> 18:12.320
studying in Nanwu,

18:12.400 --> 18:13.880
and pursuing their dreams.

18:13.960 --> 18:15.880
So, he's spent money

18:15.960 --> 18:17.320
to buy their old house back.

18:17.400 --> 18:20.240
He even got
those vintage pieces of furniture

18:20.320 --> 18:22.320
and redecorated the house.

18:23.400 --> 18:25.200
Why? To recreate memories?

18:25.280 --> 18:28.680
He must want to retire there with Grandma.

18:28.760 --> 18:31.560
That place holds
their most beautiful memories.

18:32.280 --> 18:34.360
He wants to preserve those memories

18:34.440 --> 18:35.960
while he still has money.

18:36.040 --> 18:37.640
He's always thinking about that stuff.

18:38.160 --> 18:39.720
He's getting old,
coming up with all these odd ideas.

18:41.240 --> 18:42.080
Su Haoan,

18:42.680 --> 18:44.800
so this is how you see it?

18:44.880 --> 18:47.200
But he already confused Grandma,
and he won't explain.

18:47.280 --> 18:50.960
Some things can't be solved
just by talking.

18:53.440 --> 18:55.240
I don't think you've ever
really cared about them.

18:55.320 --> 18:56.520
It's not that I don't care,

18:57.040 --> 18:57.920
but over the years…

18:58.800 --> 19:01.560
I feel like our family
has this permanent wound

19:01.640 --> 19:03.680
that no one dares to talk about
and no one dares to touch!

19:09.640 --> 19:11.000
Do you know?

19:11.080 --> 19:14.600
This is probably why Grandpa refused
to talk about his illness,

19:14.680 --> 19:18.240
neglected it, and even pushed Grandma
to go on a road trip.

19:18.880 --> 19:20.720
Your family only has three people left,

19:20.800 --> 19:23.920
yet no one is willing to talk
about the past properly.

19:24.000 --> 19:26.360
How will you face the future?

19:31.280 --> 19:32.800
The other day, Grandpa came to your house.

19:32.880 --> 19:33.960
He asked me
which side of the bed I slept on.

19:34.040 --> 19:35.360
Do you usually sleep

19:35.440 --> 19:38.080
on the left side or the right?

19:38.680 --> 19:39.680
Right side.

19:40.600 --> 19:43.720
Do you know, now Grandpa always
sleeps on the left side at home,

19:43.800 --> 19:46.240
and Grandma always sleeps
on the right side?

19:46.760 --> 19:48.720
When Grandma isn't at home,

19:49.800 --> 19:51.040
I go to her room

19:51.880 --> 19:55.080
every day to clean

19:55.160 --> 19:56.280
and tidy up.

19:58.000 --> 19:59.640
Then I sit here,

20:00.520 --> 20:02.080
listening to old songs

20:02.720 --> 20:04.280
and looking at old photos.

20:04.360 --> 20:05.720
So many memories

20:06.680 --> 20:08.080
suddenly flood back.

20:08.160 --> 20:10.240
I have to hurry and write them down.

20:11.680 --> 20:13.200
Once I've written them down,

20:14.000 --> 20:16.840
I'll head back to the old house
and add more things to it.

20:18.560 --> 20:21.520
The person you want to be with
till the end is Grandma, right?

20:25.080 --> 20:28.240
Given my current physical condition,
I will definitely

20:28.960 --> 20:30.000
leave this world before her.

20:33.280 --> 20:36.120
A few years ago, I was busy with work,

20:36.880 --> 20:38.320
and I had no time to accompany her.

20:38.400 --> 20:40.280
After she retired,

20:40.960 --> 20:42.040
she spent every day

20:42.840 --> 20:44.120
just staying at home.

20:46.280 --> 20:47.640
And then,

20:47.720 --> 20:49.640
that car accident

20:49.720 --> 20:50.960
took away the happiness

20:51.560 --> 20:52.880
of the whole family.

20:55.880 --> 20:58.240
Why didn't you travel with Grandma?

20:58.840 --> 21:01.040
The two of you would have been happier.

21:02.160 --> 21:03.640
I wanted to,

21:05.400 --> 21:07.200
but my health

21:07.280 --> 21:08.960
didn't allow me to accompany her.

21:12.160 --> 21:14.240
I always feel like I owe her.

21:15.080 --> 21:16.680
So, one time,

21:16.760 --> 21:18.800
I intentionally had a big fight with her,

21:19.360 --> 21:20.400
so she'd know

21:21.040 --> 21:21.920
that she could

21:22.800 --> 21:25.280
travel alone without me.

21:27.400 --> 21:31.040
They must both have been so uncomfortable
without each other.

21:31.120 --> 21:33.120
They were just holding on.

21:33.720 --> 21:34.920
You, too.

21:35.000 --> 21:38.400
You're so young,
so you should bear the pain at home

21:38.480 --> 21:39.760
and help them move on.

21:40.440 --> 21:42.120
No one has ever talked to me
about all this.

21:44.120 --> 21:45.400
Well, I'll be the first to wake you up.

21:49.240 --> 21:50.360
What about you?

21:51.120 --> 21:52.920
Does anyone listen to you properly?

21:55.440 --> 21:56.640
This is a bridge again.

21:57.160 --> 22:00.560
The place you go to whenever
you face pressure and want to escape.

22:00.640 --> 22:01.760
So, you also have pressure,

22:02.360 --> 22:04.560
but no one listens to you properly.
Isn't that right?

22:05.960 --> 22:06.800
I have an order.

22:08.000 --> 22:09.160
Zhong Siqiao!

22:12.160 --> 22:13.480
You've helped Dian.

22:13.560 --> 22:14.720
You've helped Xiang Lang.

22:14.800 --> 22:16.400
You've helped all your family.

22:16.480 --> 22:18.320
You've helped everyone around you.

22:18.400 --> 22:19.520
You've helped me.

22:19.600 --> 22:20.520
What about you?

22:22.200 --> 22:23.800
Is there anything I can help you with?

22:28.920 --> 22:29.960
No need to smile.

22:30.800 --> 22:32.200
No need to force a smile.

22:32.840 --> 22:34.440
What I've learned over the years

22:35.200 --> 22:37.440
is that when you don't want to smile,
simply don't!

22:37.520 --> 22:38.760
I'm not as strong as you,

22:38.840 --> 22:39.960
but I understand weakness!

22:40.560 --> 22:42.480
Isn't it hard, holding on like that?

22:44.560 --> 22:47.920
I just love them so much.
I don't want them to be separated.

22:48.560 --> 22:50.600
I don't want to see
my brother fail at everything.

22:50.680 --> 22:53.520
I don't want Grandpa and Grandma
to be left alone when they're sick.

22:53.600 --> 22:55.400
I don't want Dian, Xiang Lang,

22:56.040 --> 22:58.960
or anyone around me to feel sad!

23:02.120 --> 23:04.800
I also know that you kind of like me.
I'm not stupid.

23:04.880 --> 23:07.720
But I don't want it to be
because I helped you out,

23:07.800 --> 23:09.600
and you just happened to be heartbroken,

23:09.680 --> 23:11.520
and then you thought maybe we could try.

23:11.600 --> 23:13.680
I don't want it to be like that!

23:13.760 --> 23:16.000
So, over these days,
have you thought about me?

23:18.680 --> 23:19.960
I did think about you.

23:22.000 --> 23:25.200
But I'm also really frustrated!
You've been out of touch for half a month,

23:25.280 --> 23:27.040
and I didn't want you to know
that I missed you.

23:45.680 --> 23:46.800
I…

23:47.320 --> 23:49.440
I guess I was too emotional.

23:51.680 --> 23:52.800
I…

23:53.720 --> 23:54.760
I'm okay.

23:55.960 --> 23:58.160
- That's because you're more experienced.
- Hey…

23:59.240 --> 24:01.120
Every relationship I have
is different, okay?

24:02.800 --> 24:03.920
Don't misunderstand me.

24:04.000 --> 24:05.680
I haven't agreed to date you yet.

24:06.800 --> 24:08.160
So, would you like to date me?

24:10.120 --> 24:11.600
I… I'll think about it.

24:13.480 --> 24:14.720
Zhong Siqiao,

24:15.240 --> 24:16.880
what you just said
sounded like a bad girl.

24:16.960 --> 24:19.160
But you kissed me first!

24:19.240 --> 24:20.120
But you were more aggressive!

24:22.480 --> 24:24.360
That's because you,
an experienced guy, seduced me.

24:24.440 --> 24:26.640
Fine! Let's start over!

24:26.720 --> 24:28.640
From now on, I'll officially chase you!

24:28.720 --> 24:31.440
We'll have a shared future! Is that okay?

24:31.520 --> 24:34.000
Su Haoan, calm down. Sit down!

24:45.680 --> 24:47.160
Take your time chasing me.

24:47.840 --> 24:49.880
Slowly discover my other good sides.

24:50.400 --> 24:52.520
Gradually fall for me. Is that okay?

24:56.440 --> 24:57.640
Okay.

25:28.800 --> 25:30.920
Your kissing skills are so terrible.

26:13.480 --> 26:15.000
So embarrassing.

26:43.040 --> 26:44.080
Where is he?

26:52.800 --> 26:54.880
You… Why aren't you sleeping yet?

26:54.960 --> 26:57.160
You went out this morning?

26:57.240 --> 26:58.120
My sister came.

26:58.200 --> 26:59.520
She took my graduation album before.

26:59.600 --> 27:00.680
She just came to return it.

27:01.360 --> 27:03.200
Why didn't you invite her here?

27:03.280 --> 27:04.240
She's already gone.

27:05.440 --> 27:08.640
Want to see what your boyfriend
looked like back in college?

27:16.600 --> 27:17.560
Here.

27:17.640 --> 27:18.560
WE GRADUATED!

27:19.360 --> 27:20.720
How does he look? Handsome, right?

27:24.560 --> 27:26.080
This is Su Haoan.

27:26.160 --> 27:28.480
He dyed his hair yellow back in college.

27:29.280 --> 27:30.360
This is Qian Fei.

27:32.040 --> 27:34.360
By the way, Qian Fei
is getting married on the 8th.

27:34.440 --> 27:35.280
Are you free then?

27:35.880 --> 27:37.920
I'm not sure yet. What's up?

27:38.680 --> 27:39.840
Nothing, just asking.

27:44.480 --> 27:45.680
This is Duan Jiaxu, right?

27:48.600 --> 27:49.720
He's quite handsome.

27:50.280 --> 27:51.920
He looks the same as before.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.400
Is he handsome?

27:56.920 --> 27:58.800
This picture is average.
He looks a bit silly here.

27:59.400 --> 28:00.560
No way.

28:01.400 --> 28:03.520
You can tell he's the campus heartthrob.

28:04.160 --> 28:05.840
He must've been popular with the girls.

28:07.400 --> 28:09.120
I've heard before

28:09.640 --> 28:11.360
you two were the campus heartthrobs.

28:12.960 --> 28:14.520
I never heard of that.

28:16.320 --> 28:18.360
Well, in your eyes,

28:18.440 --> 28:20.920
what's… what's so handsome about him?

28:21.640 --> 28:22.600
In what ways?

28:23.200 --> 28:25.920
He looks very sunny.
He has a youthful vibe.

28:29.080 --> 28:31.600
He's quite eye-catching in a crowd.

28:32.760 --> 28:33.880
Maybe it's

28:34.400 --> 28:36.160
because I'm not in this photo.

28:36.760 --> 28:37.640
Isn't this you?

28:42.040 --> 28:44.200
He just looks younger.

28:44.280 --> 28:45.400
Actually, he's quite old.

28:46.080 --> 28:48.480
He's older than all of us.
He belongs to the previous generation.

28:50.520 --> 28:52.160
Isn't that a bit too much?

28:53.360 --> 28:55.040
No. He's really quite old.

29:03.560 --> 29:06.440
I didn't notice that before.
Why are there so many shots of him?

29:10.160 --> 29:11.960
- Are you tired?
- I'm fine.

29:12.960 --> 29:13.840
Well,

29:13.920 --> 29:15.800
I'm tired. Maybe I should get some rest.

29:16.680 --> 29:17.840
I haven't finished looking.

29:18.800 --> 29:20.000
Maybe another day.

29:20.080 --> 29:21.040
Let's look another day.

29:21.120 --> 29:22.800
I'll go to sleep now.

29:22.880 --> 29:24.040
Good night.

29:44.400 --> 29:45.640
The door isn't locked.

29:49.720 --> 29:50.800
Are you chasing me this relentlessly?

29:54.160 --> 29:56.040
No need to knock in the future.
Just come in.

29:57.440 --> 30:00.000
I was just afraid
you might be changing clothes.

30:01.200 --> 30:02.040
So what if I was?

30:09.240 --> 30:10.560
This is for you.

30:12.760 --> 30:14.120
What's this?

30:14.200 --> 30:15.880
Your early Valentine's Day gift.

30:15.960 --> 30:17.400
Because I saw

30:17.480 --> 30:20.760
others usually have
candlelit dinners for Valentine's Day,

30:20.840 --> 30:21.920
but I don't want to do that.

30:23.120 --> 30:24.160
Because…

30:28.920 --> 30:30.280
you are special.

30:34.840 --> 30:35.920
Can I look at it?

30:46.080 --> 30:47.960
Why do you like giving me things

30:48.720 --> 30:50.040
meant for little girls?

30:50.640 --> 30:52.080
When you wear it,
you don't look like a little girl.

30:55.240 --> 30:56.080
What does the snowflake decoration mean?

30:57.320 --> 30:58.440
It's Frost's Descent,
pronounced as my name, Shuangjiang.

31:00.680 --> 31:02.200
Come on. Put this on
for your significant other.

31:16.920 --> 31:17.880
What about this one?

31:19.200 --> 31:20.480
This one is mine.

31:22.400 --> 31:23.440
Done.

31:31.520 --> 31:32.520
Is it a mulberry leaf?

32:00.720 --> 32:01.920
It's a couple's version?

32:05.680 --> 32:06.680
Alright.

32:07.200 --> 32:08.560
Today, I'll gladly play the little girl.

32:12.760 --> 32:15.000
I also have a gift for you.
It's in the first drawer.

32:20.880 --> 32:22.040
This one?

32:33.320 --> 32:34.280
Can I open it?

32:35.160 --> 32:36.040
Of course.

32:40.760 --> 32:43.280
Didn't you say
your voice recorder didn't work?

32:44.120 --> 32:46.320
But I don't know how to use this.

32:46.400 --> 32:49.000
Do I need to plug it into the computer
and listen to it?

32:49.760 --> 32:51.520
No need.
Just press this button, and it works.

32:53.520 --> 32:55.040
Try it in your room.

32:55.680 --> 32:56.520
Why?

32:57.560 --> 33:00.720
Just try it in your place.

33:01.240 --> 33:02.800
If there's a problem, we can exchange it.

33:03.480 --> 33:04.520
Alright.

33:19.120 --> 33:20.560
Wen Shuangjiang,

33:21.080 --> 33:22.600
please be safe at work.

33:22.680 --> 33:25.720
Your boyfriend wants you
to return home safely.

33:34.520 --> 33:36.960
You deserve the best.

33:39.280 --> 33:43.360
Remember, there is someone lonely at home,
waiting for your safe return.

33:46.840 --> 33:48.120
No matter what happens,

33:48.800 --> 33:50.160
I will always be with you.

34:02.040 --> 34:03.240
This is it.

34:25.880 --> 34:27.880
I spent half a year

34:28.560 --> 34:30.000
and finally managed to make this place

34:30.800 --> 34:32.560
look a bit more presentable.

34:37.040 --> 34:38.400
Your grandma

34:38.480 --> 34:40.920
has always had great taste in life.

34:41.679 --> 34:44.360
Our past life wasn't very wealthy,

34:44.440 --> 34:47.920
but our spiritual life was still rich.

34:50.480 --> 34:52.440
She loved pottery,

34:52.520 --> 34:54.880
so I placed a lot of pottery here.

34:55.600 --> 34:57.360
She also liked flowers and plants,

34:58.040 --> 35:00.880
so I often came up here
to tidy up the plants.

35:01.480 --> 35:02.600
Also,

35:02.680 --> 35:05.800
back in the day,
she had a habit of drinking coffee.

35:07.320 --> 35:10.600
Now, I've learned to brew coffee myself.

35:12.160 --> 35:15.320
No wonder, every time I bring him here,

35:15.400 --> 35:17.680
he doesn't let me come in.

35:18.360 --> 35:21.400
Turns out this place is his paradise.

35:24.040 --> 35:25.680
I was afraid I'd forget our past life.

35:26.520 --> 35:27.560
So,

35:28.600 --> 35:30.320
while tidying up,

35:30.400 --> 35:31.880
I tried to piece together

35:31.960 --> 35:35.080
the old memories.

35:35.600 --> 35:37.840
Even this sofa and cushion

35:37.920 --> 35:40.080
look very similar to what we used before.

35:40.680 --> 35:43.000
Laughter, you're back!

35:43.080 --> 35:44.480
Grandpa, I'm sorry.

35:45.080 --> 35:46.600
I didn't ask for your permission

35:46.680 --> 35:48.480
before I told Grandma about your illness.

35:49.080 --> 35:50.120
It's my fault, Grandpa.

35:50.200 --> 35:52.160
I think Grandma has the right to know.

35:52.240 --> 35:53.560
If you didn't tell her,

35:53.640 --> 35:55.360
she would be really sad.

35:56.440 --> 35:57.800
Let me ask you.

35:57.880 --> 36:00.080
Why didn't you tell me when you got sick?

36:02.080 --> 36:03.480
I just wanted you

36:03.560 --> 36:05.160
to go on a trip without any worries,

36:05.240 --> 36:07.360
to enjoy it happily.

36:07.440 --> 36:09.040
I didn't want you

36:09.120 --> 36:11.720
to lose your dreams in life.

36:16.400 --> 36:18.800
If my dreams don't include you,

36:18.880 --> 36:20.280
then what's the point?

36:21.240 --> 36:24.080
If you hadn't purposely argued with me,

36:24.160 --> 36:25.120
making me angry,

36:25.200 --> 36:28.280
how could I have gone
on a trip and left you alone?

36:30.400 --> 36:31.920
That is because I'm sick,

36:32.000 --> 36:36.280
I often forget things and get upset.

36:37.480 --> 36:41.080
I'm also worried
that my condition is getting worse.

36:41.160 --> 36:42.600
In the end,

36:43.680 --> 36:45.960
I might forget even the people around me.

36:52.680 --> 36:53.880
Don't be afraid.

36:55.440 --> 36:57.240
We will all grow old.

36:57.320 --> 36:58.400
We will all forget.

36:59.200 --> 37:02.240
But some things won't change.

37:03.320 --> 37:05.760
We are lifelong partners.

37:11.280 --> 37:12.960
We've been together for so long.

37:13.040 --> 37:14.320
Are you happy?

37:14.840 --> 37:17.200
I really want you to be happy.

37:17.920 --> 37:21.520
When I traveled alone,
I thought I would be happy.

37:22.040 --> 37:25.080
But actually, a lot of the time, I wasn't.

37:25.160 --> 37:27.840
Because I kept thinking about this family,

37:27.920 --> 37:29.520
and I kept thinking about you.

37:31.600 --> 37:32.880
When Woodie died,

37:32.960 --> 37:34.920
Ma sent me a message.

37:35.000 --> 37:36.840
I really wanted to rush back immediately.

37:36.920 --> 37:38.880
Because I realized

37:38.960 --> 37:41.920
you all are my greatest happiness.

37:43.840 --> 37:44.840
Grandpa,

37:45.840 --> 37:47.480
don't work so hard anymore.

37:47.560 --> 37:49.040
When you can't remember things,

37:49.120 --> 37:50.400
we'll help you remember.

37:52.840 --> 37:55.280
You said you have a bad memory?

37:55.360 --> 37:57.320
Look, I even forgot about this sofa.

37:57.400 --> 38:00.840
But you remembered the fabric of the sofa
and the color of these cushions.

38:00.920 --> 38:02.800
You remember it all!

38:02.880 --> 38:04.640
I'm not that amazing.

38:05.240 --> 38:07.640
I took our old photos everywhere,

38:07.720 --> 38:10.560
looking for something similar.

38:11.200 --> 38:14.440
I searched for a long time
before I found a sofa with this fabric.

38:16.000 --> 38:17.160
Alright.

38:17.240 --> 38:18.880
Now, I'm back!

38:18.960 --> 38:20.240
Really?

38:21.320 --> 38:22.880
Welcome back.

38:24.080 --> 38:25.200
Hey!

38:26.640 --> 38:27.720
Here.

38:32.840 --> 38:34.360
We haven't danced in a long time,

38:34.440 --> 38:35.280
- have we?
- Yeah.

38:36.600 --> 38:39.280
I thought you'd forgotten
we used to dance together.

39:10.800 --> 39:12.360
Sang Yan's college time

39:12.440 --> 39:14.280
was a phase I never saw

39:14.880 --> 39:17.080
and never participated in.

39:19.200 --> 39:21.200
I clearly felt an emotion

39:21.280 --> 39:23.720
that kept appearing in the past,

39:23.800 --> 39:26.320
but I never managed to capture it.

39:27.720 --> 39:30.160
Yes, I regret it.

39:31.280 --> 39:32.960
I regret it very, very much.

39:34.040 --> 39:36.520
I regret not being part
of that time in his life.

39:39.080 --> 39:40.200
If I could,

39:40.880 --> 39:43.760
I would want to participate
in every moment of his life

39:44.520 --> 39:46.960
and accompany him through every emotion.

39:48.520 --> 39:50.640
During every sad moment,

39:50.720 --> 39:53.000
I would be by his side.

39:59.880 --> 40:02.160
Of course,
I'd be happy to be your power bank,

40:04.240 --> 40:06.680
providing you with energy

40:09.560 --> 40:11.280
every day in the future.

40:37.160 --> 40:39.320
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

40:39.400 --> 40:41.480
Oh, how did you do on the exam?

40:42.440 --> 40:43.720
I performed average.

40:43.800 --> 40:44.960
It was okay.

40:45.040 --> 40:46.240
What about you?

40:51.600 --> 40:53.320
- What?
- Where's my reward?

40:54.120 --> 40:56.120
I did really well.

40:56.720 --> 40:59.200
Didn't you promise
that if I performed above expectations,

40:59.280 --> 41:00.240
you'd give me a reward?

41:09.320 --> 41:10.640
What's wrong?

41:11.480 --> 41:13.440
I'm out of power. I need a recharge.

41:16.440 --> 41:18.800
Your reward will be my endless energy.

41:25.880 --> 41:28.000
Well… Open your hands.

41:48.680 --> 41:49.720
What do you mean?

41:54.200 --> 41:55.240
Charging.

41:56.040 --> 41:57.160
You…

41:57.240 --> 41:59.400
You promised me a reward. Give it now.

42:01.560 --> 42:03.840
Sir, what are you laughing at?

42:04.600 --> 42:06.440
I'm laughing because
you young people are so lucky,

42:06.960 --> 42:08.000
full of energy.

42:21.720 --> 42:23.720
Well, consider it a debt.

42:25.440 --> 42:27.600
From now on, you'll be my…

42:28.360 --> 42:29.320
power bank.

45:21.480 --> 45:22.600
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:22.680 --> 45:23.720
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
